\i\b Underscores
\i0\b0  only allowed to designate order, 0_, 1_, 2_ etc.  These are reserved for the system and won\'92t appear to the user or can screw up the linking system if used otherwise. \
Never use underscores like Time__Rhythm vs Time__Automation.  Instead use \'93\'85\'93, e.g. Time\'85Rhythm and Time\'85Automation\
